C.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    Not informing the employees that they are going to be monitored could be an invasion of privacy.                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"D\">                                                                  D.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    The network could still experience traffic slow down.                                                      </li>                                                                                                ', 'C', NULL, NULL),
