('Question #228', 'What firewall evasion scanning technique make use of a zombie system that has low network activity as well as its fragment identification numbers?<br>', '                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"A\">                                                                  A.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    Packet fragmentation scanning                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"B\">                                                                  B.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    Spoof source address scanning                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"C\">                                                                  C.                                                              </span>                                                         