HTTP/1.1 Host westbank.com</li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"D\">                                                                  D.                                                              </span>GET /restricted/ HTTP/1.1 Host: westbank.com                                                      </li>                                                                                                ', 'C', NULL, NULL),
