                    C.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    -sX                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"D\">                                                                  D.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    -sF                                                      </li>                                                                                                ', 'B', NULL, NULL),
('Question #376', 'A security analyst uses Zenmap to perform an ICMP timestamp ping scan to acquire information related to the current time from the target host machine.<br>Which of the following Zenmap options must the analyst use to perform the ICMP timestamp ping scan?<br>', '                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"A\">                                                                  A.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    -Pn                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"B\">                                                                  B.                                                              </span>                                                                                                                    -PU                                                      </li>                                                                                                        <li class=\"multi-choice-item correct-hidden\">                                                                                                                        <span class=\"multi-choice-letter\" data-choice-letter=\"C\">                                                                  C.                                                        